Apparatus criticus

  • Text from autopsy;
  • 1: Biondi: ........; on the stone, traces of a stroke descending lower right (Χ, Σ, Κ, Ε all seem possible) and then two vertical strokes the first close to the preceding stroke, the second well separated.
